”Alexa, ask Mars facts to give me a fact”
”Alexa, tell Mars facts to tell me a mars fact.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mars facts
des: This skill "Mars Facts" is for those who wants to go deep in mars exploration. This skill features many different mars facts. User can simply start the skill by saying, " Alexa, Open Mars Facts" and later on Alexa will reply back with different mars fact. The facts are randomized so whenever asked Alexa will reply with a completely different fact.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
